CustomField.description: Overall comments: Is this group strategic in terms of our own internal strategy for movement building? Why is a grant timely and/or important to the movement at this time? If this is a new group, provide rationale behind the decision to fund it now. If group is a renewal, include how the group has evolved over time and describe how or why not. Also include rationale for grant size. (Rationale for support)
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Overall comments: Is group strategic for movement building? Is grant timely/important? If new, rationale to fund now. If renewal, how group has evolved or why not. Also rationale for grant size.
